'''Evocii''' was the native language of the [[Evocii]] species from [[Nal Hutta/Legends|Nal Hutta]], previously known as Evocar. Evocii lived under the surface of the fifth moon of Nal Hutta, [[Nar Shaddaa/Legends|Nar Shaddaa]], having little interaction with other species. [[Hutt/Legends|Hutts]] believed them extinct long ago.

Most Evocii were fluent in both Evocii and [[Galactic Basic Standard/Legends|Basic]], although they were only literate in their own language. Some Evocii were also fluent in [[Huttese/Legends|Huttese]].

''Choowahai'' means ''Hello.

